trans-unit.source: • The Test Explorer now has significant UI improvements including better handling of large test sets, more filtering, commands, and the addition of customizable columns.

trans-unit.target: • Access the Developer Command Prompt and Developer PowerShell by either going to “Tools > Command Line” or by searching for them via the Visual Studio Search.

trans-unit.source: • You can now set a breakpoint in a JavaScript application and start a debug session using Microsoft Edge Insider browser.
